            <title>[CXF-1571] CachedOutputStream#writeCacheTo(StringBuilder, int) fails with StringIndexOutOfBoundsException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-1571</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;    public void writeCacheTo(StringBuilder out, int limit) throws IOException {&lt;br/&gt;
    ...&lt;br/&gt;
                if ((count + x) &amp;gt; limit) &lt;/p&gt;
{
                    x = count - limit;                               &amp;lt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; this has to be:    x = limit - count;
                }
&lt;p&gt;                out.append(new String(bytes, 0, x));&lt;br/&gt;
                count += x;&lt;br/&gt;
    ...&lt;br/&gt;
    }&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If limit is reached x becomes negative and String construction fails with&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;java.lang.StringIndexOutOfBoundsException: String index out of range: -784&lt;br/&gt;
	at java.lang.String.checkBounds(String.java:368)&lt;br/&gt;
	at java.lang.String.&amp;lt;init&amp;gt;(String.java:457)&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.cxf.io.CachedOutputStream.writeCacheTo(CachedOutputStream.java:272)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
